race.comment: NINA SIYAN (5) broke from the inside draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only one length (19.97) behind Goldstar Chanel at Q Lakeside. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Top chance in this line up. BONNIE'S WAY (3) filled a minor placing last start at Q Lakeside behind Hara's Jackson (22.71) in a Grade 6. Has the pace to be prominent. Expected to feature again. BARRY THE BOSS (1) turned in a moderate run last time when sixth at Capalaba over 366m behind Idea's Man (20.68) in a Grade 6. Was in the money prior to that. The form out of his last race has been franked. Can measure up this time. RING THAT BELLE (2) has definite claims at her first try at this circuit.
